25
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:41,248
From majestic mountains
and crystal-clear lakes,

26
00:01:41,248 --> 00:01:43,120
to dramatic coastlines,

27
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,720
and ancient forests.

28
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:47,520
