unforgettable memories.

30
00:01:49,984 --> 00:01:52,280
And we warmly welcome
more visitors from China

31
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,000
to come and explore New Zealand.

32
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,200
Our doors are always open.

33
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,640
And we really look forward
to seeing you here.

